Cem%3E%20and%20former%20human%20resources%20director%20at%20PwC%2C%20British%20Airways%2C%20and%20DPD%20in%20Ireland.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20promotion%20might%20mean%20a%20new%20job%20title%20or%20an%20increase%20in%20status%2C%20it%20could%20also%20represent%20a%20pay%20rise%20or%20bring%20an%20improvement%20in%20your%20benefits%20package.%20A%20promotion%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20progress%2C%20of%20improvement%2C%20and%20sometimes%20of%20vindication.%20It's%20recognition%20that%20hard%20work%20pays%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20are%20promoted%20for%20different%20reasons.%20They%20might%20have%20achieved%20a%20new%20professional%20qualification%2C%20like%2C%20for%20those%20in%20accountancy%2C%20law%20or%20medicine.%20It%20could%20come%20because%20you've%20met%20milestones%2C%20brought%20in%20new%20customers%2C%20or%20received%20positive%20feedback%20from%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEither%20way%2C%20here%20are%20six%20signs%20that%20you%20might%20be%20heading%20toward%20a%20promotion%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222c383e2f-3971-4f32-b1cd-d5d576147cf7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChanges%20within%20your%20organization%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELook%20out%20for%20shifts%20in%20your%20company.%20Is%20it%20expanding%20or%20restructuring%2C%20or%20is%20your%20boss%20being%20promoted%3F%20Changes%20in%20an%20organization%20throw%20up%20opportunities%20all%20the%20time%2C%20and%20you%20may%20be%20unexpectedly%20earmarked%20for%20a%20new%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20some%20mature%20organizations%2C%20the%20chain%20of%20succession%20could%20be%20more%20concrete.%20My%20second%20job%2C%20for%20example%2C%20was%20at%20Ford%20Motor%20Company%2C%20which%20was%20a%20highly%20structured%20organization%20where%20your%20career%20was%20mapped%20out%20for%20the%20next%20five%20to%2010%20years.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20approach%20works%20in%20some%20companies%2C%20but%20it%20has%20a%20habit%20of%20coming%20asunder%20when%20life%20gets%20in%20the%20way.%20%3Cspan%3EI%20think%20there's%20a%20balance%20to%20be%20struck%20between%20mapping%20everything%20out%20and%20being%20flexible.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20for%20many%20companies%20workplace%20reorganization%20creates%20space%20for%20promotions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b5ff95b2-72c8-4148-bcdc-294d2df58d93%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPositive%20feedback%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20should%20be%20having%20regular%20performance%20management%20discussions.%20If%20you're%20receiving%20positive%20feedback%20there%2C%20it%20will%20give%20you%20an%20indication%20of%20whether%20your%20employer%20is%20happy%20with%20your%20work.%20You%20might%20be%20asked%20about%20your%20career%20goals%2C%20too%2C%20which%20can%20be%20a%20promising%20sign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed610746-e0ae-4b5f-9f8f-9611041caa76%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeing%20asked%20to%20represent%20your%20company%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESenior%20managers%20might%20encourage%20you%20to%20attend%20exhibitions%20or%20get%20involved%20in%20extra-curricular%20activities%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20company.%20They%20might%20request%20that%20you%20act%20as%20an%20ambassador%20for%20the%20organization%2C%20or%20you%20might%20find%20yourself%20being%20asked%20to%20speak%20at%20events.%20While%20it's%20no%20guarantee%20of%20a%20promotion%2C%20it's%20further%20evidence%20that%20you're%20valued%20at%20work%20and%20may%20be%20considered%20for%20one%20when%20it%20comes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2255d7fc29-5c76-4cc3-8b6e-23f4f61824b5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeing%20introduced%20to%20new%20people%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20sought%20out%20to%20meet%20new%20people%2C%20whether%20that's%20invitations%20to%20meetings%20or%20introductions%20to%20customers%2C%20is%20another%20important%20indication%20that%20your%20opinions%20and%20contribution%20to%20the%20company%20are%20valued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b87fb0e0-8fce-43e5-9056-abd6fdec9f1b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeing%20asked%20for%20your%20input%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20boss%20often%20asks%20for%20your%20opinion%2C%20it's%20a%20positive%20sign.%20It%20shows%20that%20they%20respect%20your%20judgment%20and%20appreciate%20your%20feedback.%20Use%20these%20as%20opportunities%20to%20take%20initiative%20and%20prove%20your%20worth%20to%20your%20manager.%20%3Cspan%3EDo%20so%20in%20a%20subtle%20way%3A%20volunteering%2C%20writing%20proposals%2C%20or%20taking%20on%20additional%20responsibilities.%20Never%20forget%20that%20making%20your%20boss%20look%20good%20is%20a%20great%20way%20to%20set%20yourself%20apart.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f88a9ce2-0e15-4630-bd57-ce447c972e4d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETaking%20on%20extra%20responsibility%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20asked%20to%20take%20on%20extra%20responsibility%20is%20another%20signal%20that%20you're%20eligible%20for%20a%20promotion.%20Common%20examples%20of%20this%20are%20being%20asked%20to%20take%20on%20more%20work%20or%20new%20clients.%20Alternatively%2C%20you%20might%20be%20asked%20to%20mentor%20less%20experienced%20members%20of%20the%20team%20or%20lead%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20a%20promotion%2C%20you%20should%20be%20looking%20to%20take%20on%20more%20responsibility%20all%20the%20time%2C%20as%20it%20shows%20a%20willingness%20to%20learn%20and%20add%20value.%20Being%20given%20a%20new%20responsibility%20is%20an%20opportunity%20for%20managers%20to%20assess%20your%20suitability%20for%20a%20new%20role.%20And%20for%20you%2C%20it's%20a%20chance%20to%20prove%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f60f65b2-4dff-4ba8-9141-d4b77ae12429%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAsking%20for%20a%20promotion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20unsure%20whether%20you're%20up%20for%20a%20promotion%2C%20ask%20your%20boss%20directly.%20Too%20often%2C%20employees%20assume%20their%20manager%20knows%20they%20want%20to%20be%20promoted.%20People%20who%20are%20consistently%20striving%20for%20promotions%20should%20have%20a%20clear%20conversation%20about%20promotions%20at%20least%20once%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20advice%20is%20to%20ask%20your%20boss%2C%20%26quot%3BCan%20we%20have%20a%20conversation%20about%20me%20and%20where%20I'm%20at%3F%26quot%3B%20This%20conversation%20might%20be%20during%20an%20appraisal%20discussion%2C%20it%20might%20come%20up%20in%20a%20car%20journey%2C%20or%20even%20subtly%20over%20coffee.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20be%20direct%3A%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20you%20think%20you're%20ready%20for%20advancement%20and%20put%20a%20business%20case%20forward%20as%20to%20why%20you%20should%20be%20considered.%20After%20the%20discussion%2C%20get%20it%20documented%20in%20writing%20where%20you%20want%20to%20be%20and%20how%20quickly%20you%20want%20to%20get%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aa163ab4-03c3-4f36-975b-3809fdeae426%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20you%20accept%20a%20promotion%20if%20it's%20offered%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20times%2C%20we%20have%20a%20classic%20conundrum%20where%20someone%20is%20asked%20to%20do%20a%20different%20role%20overnight%20with%20little%20preparation.%20A%20promotion%20may%20not%20always%20be%20right%20for%20you%2C%20and%20you%20may%20not%20choose%20to%20accept%20one%20if%20it's%20offered.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20the%20degree%20of%20ambition%2C%20I%20generally%20advise%20accepting%20the%20promotion%20and%20paddling%20very%2C%20very%20hard%20underwater%20while%20asking%20for%20training%2C%20support%2C%20and%20guidance%20to%20help%20you%20thrive%20in%20your%20new%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-tell-signs-getting-promotion-hr-exec-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734088222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675