2%3A%22Superstar%20Allu%20Arjun%20Arrested%3A%20What%20Are%20The%20Charges%20Against%20Him%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETelugu%20actor%20Allu%20Arjun%20has%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20police%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20death%20of%20a%20woman%20during%20the%20premiere%20of%20his%20latest%20movie%20'Pushpa%202%3A%20The%20Rise'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2035-year-old%20woman%20was%20killed%20and%20her%20nine-year-old%20son%20was%20seriously%20injured%20during%20the%20premiere%20of%20'Pushpa%202%3A%20The%20Rule'%20at%20a%20theatre%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20December%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20at%20Hyderabad's%20Sandhya%20Theatre%20as%20massive%20crowds%20thronged%20the%20venue%20to%20catch%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20film's%20lead%20actor%2C%20Allu%20Arjun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20charges%20against%20Allu%20Arjun%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20had%20registered%20a%20case%20under%20sections%20105%20(Culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder)%2C%20118(1)%20(Voluntarily%20causing%20hurt)%20r%2Fw%203(5)%20BNS%20against%20Allu%20Arjun%2C%20his%20security%20team%20and%20the%20management%20of%20the%20theatre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20registered%20at%20Chikkadpally%20Police%20Station%20on%20December%205%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20the%20woman's%20husband.%20The%20police%20arrested%20the%20theatre%20owner%2C%20general%20manager%20and%20security%20manager%20on%20December%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2011%2C%20the%20actor%20approached%20the%20Telangana%20High%20Court%2C%20seeking%20orders%20to%20quash%20the%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20there%20was%20no%20intimation%20from%20theatre%20management%20or%20the%20actor's%20team%20that%20they%20would%20be%20visiting%20the%20theatre.%20The%20theatre%20management%20also%20did%20not%20make%20any%20additional%20provisions%20regarding%20security%20to%20manage%20the%20crowd.%3