e%20Constitution%2C%20said%20Union%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20as%20he%20began%20a%20debate%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%20%26quot%3BThere%20have%20always%20been%20attempts%20by%20a%20particular%20party%20to%20hijack%20and%20appropriate%20the%20work%20of%20Constitution-making.%20Mr%20Speaker%2C%20all%20these%20things%20related%20to%20the%20history%20of%20Constitution%20Making%20in%20India%20have%20been%20hidden%20from%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Defence%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20marks%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20on%20November%2026%2C%201949.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20his%20speech%2C%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said%20that%20they%20keep%20the%20Constitution%20in%20their%20pockets%20while%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20carry%20it%20in%20their%20hearts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20the%20Congress%2C%20we%20have%20never%20used%20the%20Constitution%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20achieve%20political%20gains.%20We%20have%20lived%20the%20Constitution.%20We%20have%20faced%20the%20conspiracies%20being%20hatched%20against%20the%20Constitution%20like%20a%20vigilant%20and%20true%20soldier.%20And%20have%20even%20endured%20great%20hardships%20to%20protect%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20mention%20of%20Veer%20Savarkar%20while%20remembering%20the%20architects%20of%20the%20Constitution%20sparked%20an%20uproar%20from%20the%20Opposition%20benches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20speech%20also%20mentioned%20Justice%20HR%20Khanna%2C%20a%20former%20judge%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20whose%20dissenting%20judgment%20during%20the%20Emergency%20imposed%20by%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%20in%201976%20had%20cost%20him%20the%20Chief%20Justice's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20also%20referred%20to%20instances%20where%20he%20said%20judges%20had%20to%20pay%20a%20heavy%20cost%20for%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Blimit%20the%20powers%20of%20a%20dictatorial%20government%20within%20the%20constitutional%20limits%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%201973%2C%20ignoring%20all%20constitutional%20values%2C%20the%20then%20Congress%20government%20superseded%20Justice%20JM%20Shelat%2C%20KS%20Hegde%2C%20and%20AN%20Grover%20and%20appointed%20the%20fourth%20most%20senior%20judge%20as%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734076140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fmnte4l6g_rajnath-singh-in-lok-sabha_625x300_13_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajnath-singh-says-attempts-to-black-out-role-of-some-in-upholding-constitution-during-debate-in-lok-sabha-7238210%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20have%20been%20attempts%20to%20black%20out%20the%20role%20of%20some%20in%20upholding%20the%20Constitution%2C%20said%20Union%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20as%20he%20began%20a%20debate%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20mark%20the%2075%20years%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajnath-singh-says-attempts-to-black-out-role-of-some-in-upholding-constitution-during-debate-in-lok-sabha-7238210%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Allu%20Arjun%20arrested%20post%20tragic%20stampede%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734075707000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116282044%2Cimgsize-519017.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftelugu%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fallu-arjun-arrested-following-tragic-stampede-at-pushpa-2-premiere%2Farticleshow%2F116282060.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116282060.cms%5C%22