ly%20scarce%20here.%20Even%20tubewells%20meant%20for%20drinking%20water%20are%20out%20of%20reach%20for%20most%20people%20%E2%80%94%20only%20wealthy%20families%20can%20afford%20them.%20Drilling%20a%20well%20costs%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%202%20to%203%20lakh%2C%20making%20it%20unaffordable%20for%20the%20poorer%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Mrinal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAccessibility%20to%20freshwater%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20health%20and%20sanitation%20issues%2C%20including%20menstrual%20hygiene%2C%20SEED%20focuses%20on%20increasing%20freshwater%20access%20as%20a%20strategic%20approach%20to%20address%20the%20complex%20issues%20affecting%20the%20mangrove%20forest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Integrated%20Coastal%20Zone%20Management%20Programme%20was%20executed%20in%20Sagar%20Island%2C%20where%20Soma%20lives.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20programme%2C%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20World%20Bank%2C%20we%20started%20pond%20excavation.%20After%20the%20excavation%2C%20the%20embankments%20of%20the%20ponds%20were%20made%20a%20little%20higher%20so%20that%20saltwater%20intrusion%20does%20not%20happen%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Mrinal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20worked%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20people%2C%20turning%20out%20to%20be%20a%20success.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20cyclones%2C%20where%20saltwater%20intrusion%20was%20common%2C%20these%20ponds%20with%20higher%20embankments%20were%20left%20untouched.%20In%20Ghoramara%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20dug%20similar%20ponds%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Mrinal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-07-at-11.04.02_94fd4213_11zon-1733483303-500x375-1-1733976864.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebe