%2C%20which%20was%20implemented%20on%20a%20regular%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20agencies%20such%20as%20PHEs%20and%20their%20support%20have%20allowed%20them%20to%20successfully%20bring%20drinking%20water%20to%20every%20household.%20Additionally%2C%20SEED%20also%20helped%20dig%20tubewells%20to%20increase%20access%20to%20freshwater.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSEED%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20started%20with%20the%20establishment%20of%20such%20tubewells%2C%20and%20people%20are%20now%20using%20the%20groundwater.%20This%20has%20been%20immensely%20beneficial%20for%20us%2C%20and%20we%20have%20water%20lines%20connecting%20to%20taps%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Soma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMenstrual%20health%20management%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20efforts%20to%20combat%20freshwater%20scarcity%20have%20provided%20some%20relief%2C%20the%20silent%20struggle%20of%20women%20in%20the%20Sundarbans%20continues.%20Bound%20by%20cultural%20taboos%20surrounding%20menstruation%2C%20women%20face%20significant%20challenges%20during%20their%20menstrual%20cycles.%20These%20taboos%20often%20leave%20them%20isolated%20and%20vulnerable%2C%20complicating%20their%20plight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaleya%20Bibi%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Jharkhali%20Island%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20tear%20sarees%20into%20strips%20and%20use%20them%20during%20my%20periods%20because%20pads%20were%20either%20too%20expensive%20or%20unavailable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20story%20is%20not%20unique%20%E2%80%94%20millions%20of%20women%20across%20India%20face%20similar%20struggles.%20According%20to%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20(2015-16)%2C%20only%2036%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20336%20million%20menstruating%20girls%20and%20women%20had%20access%20to%20sanitary%20napkins%20and%20practised%20proper%20hygiene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinancial%20constraints%20force%20women%20to%20rely%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246267%2Fmenstrual-hygiene-kit-cloth-pads-avni-safepads-women-health-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecloth%20instead%20of%20sanitary%20pads%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20this%20practice%20comes%20with%20its%20own%20dangers.%20Cloths%2C%20which%20need%20sunlight%20to%20dry%20properly%20and%20eliminate%20germs%2C%20are%20often%20dried%20indoors%20in%20dark%2C%20humid%20spaces%20due%20to%20cultural%20taboos%20around%20menstruation.%20This%20leads%20to%20severe%20infections%2C%20adversely%20affecting%20their%20reproductive%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20addressing%20women%E2%80%99s%20health%2C%20the%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20team%20had%20identified%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20problems%20stemmed%20from%20vaginal%20infections%20and%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20this%20was%20unhygienic%20menstrual%20practices%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Mrinal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCleaning%20themselves%20with%20highly%20saline%20water%20during%20their%20periods%20leads%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F278327%2Fmumbai-microbiologist-innovates-spray-prevent-uti-public-toilet-hygiene%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUrinary%20Tract%20Infections%20(UTI)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Pelvic%20Inflammatory%20Diseases%20(PID)%2C%20and%20vaginal%20infections%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Alima%20Ahmad%2C%20the%20grant%20writer%20at%20SEED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrinal%20highlights%20the%20sad%20reality%20faced%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20awareness%20among%20the%20masses.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20ignore%20the%20disease%20and%20continue%20with%20their%20everyday%20lives.%20For%20some%20it%20becomes%20serious%2C%20for%20others%2C%20they%20get%20cured.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disposal%20of%20used%20cloths%20was%20another%20significant%20challenge.%20Many%20women%20discard%20the%20cloths%20in%20rivers%20or%20other%20open%20water%20bodies%2C%20which%20not%20only%20pollutes%20the%20environment%20but%20also%20exposes%20them%20to%20additional%20health%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20women%20would%20hide%20their%20menstruation.%20They%20would%20not%20want%20to%20talk%20about%20it%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20they%20would%20not%20even%20let%20their%20husbands%20know%20that%20they%20were%20menstruating%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Soma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20could%20not%20ask%20my%20husband%20to%20buy%20pads%2C%20nor%20can%20I%20go%20myself.%20I%20was%20worried%20about%20what%20others%20might%20think%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saleya%2C%20echoing%20the%20mindset%20of%20many%20women%20in%20her%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBreaking%20the%20taboo%3A%20%E2%80%98Today%2C%20almost%20every%20woman%20uses%20sanitary%20napkins%20regularly%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECreating%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20women%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F384653%2Fsandy-khanda-menstrual-hygiene-green-pencil-foundation-climate-change%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopenly%20discuss%20menstruation%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20a%20crucial%20first%20step.%20As%20Alima%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CBreaking%20the%20taboo%20was%20a%20significant%20challenge%2C%20requiring%20considerable%20effort%20than%20expected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20association%20with%20the%20%3Cem%3EPanchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Self%20Help%20Groups%20(SHGs)%20and%20Community-Based%20Organisations%20(CBO)%2C%20SEED%20focused%20on%20conducting%20workshops%20and%20awareness%20programmes%20on%20a%20fortnightly%20basis%20around%20menstrual%20health%20management%2C%20which%20was%20an%20eye-opener%20for%20rural%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERituporna%20Nath%2C%20the%20communications%20manager%20at%20SEED%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20people%20were%20reluctant%20to%20attend%20these%20workshops.%20But%20as%20days%20passed%2C%20they%20were%20inspired%20by%20other%20women%20who%20benefited.%E2%80%9D%3C