%2Fbutter-chicken-in-delhi-2-1733746662.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20butter%20chicken%20served%20at%20Baba's%20in%20Delhi's%20Defence%20Colony%20has%20velvety%20notes%20with%20a%20creamy%20flavour%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fbutter-chicken-in-delhi-2-1733746662.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fbutter-chicken-in-delhi-2-1733746662-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fbutter-chicken-in-delhi-2-1733746662-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fbutter-chicken-in-delhi-2-1733746662-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fbutter-chicken-in-delhi-2-1733746662-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-387675%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20butter%20chicken%20served%20at%20Baba%E2%80%99s%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Defence%20Colony%20has%20velvety%20notes%20with%20a%20creamy%20flavour%3B%20Pictures%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbabasrestaurant_%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBabas%20Restaurant%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20a%20good%20helping%20of%20the%20dish%2C%20you%20can%20head%20to%20Baba%E2%80%99s%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Defence%20Colony.%20On%20most%20days%2C%20you%20can%20find%20Chef%20Jatin%20Mallick%2C%20co-founder%2C%20Dos%20by%20Tres%2C%20Delhi%2C%20grabbing%20his%20fill%20of%20the%20dish%2C%20here.%20While%20many%20recipes%20end%20up%20calling%20for%20copious%20amounts%20of%20cream%20and%20tomatoes%20(for%20the%20sweet%20flavour%20and%20the%20red%20hue)%2C%20the%20rendition%20at%20Baba%E2%80%99s%20manages%20to%20make%20it%20a%20perfect%20balance.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Havemore%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20butter%20chicken%2C%20but%20the%20chicken%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20popular%20curry%20%3Cem%3Emasala%20%3C%2Fem%3Emade%20with%20boneless%20chicken)%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F44188%2Fsoup-em-spice-em-sprout-em-10-must-try-lentil-dishes-from-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Edal%20makhani%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20North%20Indian%20dish%20%3C%2Fa%3Emade%20with%20black%20lentils%20and%20red%20kidney%20beans)%20are%20a%20must-have%20at%20the%20restaurant.%20The%20journey%20of%20the%20eatery%20from%20a%20tea%20stall%20that%20was%20born%20in%201959%20to%20the%20now-famous%20multicrore%20restaurant%20chain%20has%20gone%20down%20in%20culinary%20archives.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FlnUAJuNSeYA%3Fsi%3DoZ9ynNJFgj_GGGrb%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20Chef%20Jatin%2C%20this%20place%20features%20on%20his%20list%20of%20favourites.%20Not%20just%20this%20eatery%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPandara%20Road%20has%20been%20a%20go-to%20spot%20for%20ages.%20Whenever%20I%20used%20to%20visit%20Delhi%2C%20a%20visit%20to%20Pandara%20Road%20with%20the%20family%20was%20a%20must.%20That%20flavour%20of%20butter%20chicken%20is%20etched%20in%20my%20head.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Moti%20Mahal%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20OG%20butter%20chicken%20spot!%20It%20was%20here%20that%20the%20seminal%20discovery%20happened%20post-Partition.%20The%20story%20goes%20that%20Kundan%20Lal%20Gujral%2C%20a%20cloth%20merchant%E2%80%99s%20son%20began%20working%20at%20an%20eatery%20in%20Peshawar%E2%80%99s%20Gora%20Bazaar%20(in%20present-day%20Pakistan)%20in%20the%20early%201900s.%20After%20Partition%2C%20in%201947%2C%20Kundan%20Lal%20Gujral%20travelled%20to%20Delhi%20with%20his%20family%20as%20refugees%2C%20where%20Kundan%20reestablished%20Moti%20Mahal%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Daryaganj.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20history%20tells%20us%2C%20the%20butter%20chicken%20was%20born%20out%20of%20the%20worry%20of%20having%20cooked%20chicken%20dry%20out.%20Kundan%20was%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20a%20sauce%20with%20which%20he%20could%20rehydrate%20them.%20His%20solution%20lay%20in%20the%20butter%20sauce%2C%20which%20eventually%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356862%2Forigin-story-chicken-tikka-masala-history-shish-mahal-scotland-glasgow-karims-delhi-ranveer-brar-recipe%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egave%20history%20its%20best%20dish%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%201950s%20heyday%2C%20Gujral%E2%80%99s%20Moti%20Mahal%20was%20extremely%20popular%20with%20celebrities%20and%20world%20leaders%2C%20including%20Zakir%20Hussain%2C%20Jawahar%20Lal%20Nehru%2C%20Richard%20Nixon%20and%20John%20F%20Kennedy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fbutter-chicken-in-delhi-3-1733747210.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Moti%20Mahal%20in%20Daryaganj%2C%20Delhi%20was%20the%20birthplace%20of%20the%20butter%20chicken%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fbutter-chicken-in-delhi-3-1733747210.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fbutter-chicken-in-delhi-3-1733747210-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fbutter-chicke