%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emade%20from%20cow%20dung%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20cow%20urine%2C%20and%20natural%20jaggery.%20We%20only%20support%20farming%20that%20avoids%20chemicals%2C%20helping%20our%20farmers%20grow%20crops%20in%20the%20most%20environmentally%20friendly%20way%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EVenturing%20into%20%E2%80%98ready-to-eat%E2%80%99%20items%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20greater%20control%20over%20the%20quality%20and%20authenticity%20of%20their%20products%2C%20Sreshte%20expanded%20its%20operations%20by%20setting%20up%20a%20dedicated%20processing%20unit%20and%20warehouse%20in%20Manikanta%E2%80%99s%20village%2C%20Lachannagudipudi.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%2C%20Subbarao%20%3Cem%3EGaru%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20oversees%20the%20processing%20unit%20in%20our%20village.%20He%20has%20been%20a%20great%20pillar%20of%20support%20throughout%20this%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Manikanta.%20While%20the%20processing%20of%20products%20takes%20place%20at%20their%20facility%20in%20the%20village%2C%20the%20packaging%20and%20delivery%20operations%20are%20managed%20at%20their%20store%20in%20Guntur%2C%20ensuring%20a%20seamless%20transition%20from%20production%20to%20customer.%20%E2%80%9CBoth%20Pavani%20and%20I%20take%20care%20of%20the%20packing%20and%20delivery%20personally%2C%20ensuring%20everything%20is%20in%20line%20with%20our%20commitment%20to%20quality%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20satisfaction%20in%20knowing%20that%20the%20food%20we%20create%20is%20improving%20people%E2%80%99s%20health%2C%20and%20the%20positive%20feedback%20we%20receive%20each%20day%20keeps%20me%20inspired%20to%20keep%20doing%20better.%20Working%20with%20Sreshte%20has%20had%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20me%2C%20it%20has%20not%20only%20kept%20me%20active%20but%20has%20also%20improved%20my%20own%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Subbarao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20clas