%5C%22%3EAfter%20years%20of%20persistence%2C%20the%20couple%20proudly%20opened%20their%20first%20official%20Sreshte%20store%20in%20Guntur%20in%202019%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20demand%20for%20organic%20products%20continues%20to%20grow%2C%20Sreshte%20has%20expanded%20its%20product%20range%20to%20include%20over%20160%20items.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20we%20offer%20everything%20from%20organic%20rice%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328846%2Fsibi-manivannan-runs-gramiya-cold-pressed-oils-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecold-pressed%20oils%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20homemade%20powders%20like%20peanut%20and%20sprouted%20ragi%20powder%2C%20along%20with%20Himalayan%20pink%20salt%2C%20black%20salt%2C%20and%20a%20variety%20of%20flakes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manikanta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20essentials%2C%20Sreshte%20has%20ventured%20into%20ready-to-eat%20items.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20recently%20started%20offering%20homemade%20sweets%2C%20snacks%2C%20and%20cupcakes%20made%20from%20millets%2C%20jaggery%2C%20and%20palm%20jaggery%20%E2%80%94%20healthy%20alternatives%20to%20rice%20flour%2C%20refined%20flour%2C%20and%20white%20sugar%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Manikanta.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20customers%20are%20keen%20on%20organic%20products%2C%20but%20they%20often%20struggle%20to%20trust%20their%20authenticity.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20we%20invite%20them%20to%20visit%20the%20farms%2C%20and%20if%20they%20wish%2C%20they%20can%20directly%20order%20from%20the%20farmers%2C%20with%20us%20handling%20the%20delivery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESreshte%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20authenticity%20is%20reflected%20in%20their%20traditional%20processing%20methods.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20vacuum%20packing%20and%20oxygen%20absorbers%20to%20prevent%20pests%20naturally%2C%20without%20relying%20on%20preservatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manikanta.%2