es%20and%20chilli%20powder%20directly%20to%20customers.%20I%20am%20committed%20to%20continuing%20this%20path%20and%20am%20proud%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20organic%20farming%20community%20with%20Sreshte%E2%80%99s%20support.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20true%20measure%20of%20Sreshte%E2%80%99s%20success%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20stories%20of%20its%20customers.%20Nandana%2C%20a%20regular%20shopper%20from%20Rajendranagar%2C%20Guntur%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20prefer%20Sreshte%E2%80%99s%20organic%20foods%20because%20they%20are%20free%20from%20harmful%20chemicals%2C%20pesticides%2C%20and%20artificial%20additives.%20I%20can%20taste%20the%20difference%2C%20the%20food%20is%20fresh%20and%20the%20natural%20flavours%20are%20distinctive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202704px)%20100vw%2C%202704px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181106-1_11zon-1733395975.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222704%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sreshte%20ensures%20that%20farmers%20can%20sell%20their%20produce%20at%20premium%20prices%20by%20providing%20better%20market%20access%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181106-1_11zon-1733395975.jpg%202704w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181106-1_11zon-1733395975-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181106-1_11zon-1733395975-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181106-1_11zon-1733395975-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181106-1_11zon-1733395975-1536x1151.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181106-1_11zon-1733395975-2048x1535.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A